{"tid":1559200,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇渠道可以直接幫到啲走投無路嘅義士","createTime":"2019-09-10T16:53:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-11T11:29:10.000Z","uid":33769,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"91cdda22fb269060de389e34094eeb6cea7701e1","tid":1559200,"uid":33769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T16:53:47.000Z","msg":"成日聽到啲義士俾屋企人趕出門口，無地方落腳<br />\n無錢食飯（聽過啲義士靠人捐月餅醫肚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n無錢睇醫生（係晴朗聽到啲義士堅持要比診金，得唔到最及時嘅治療<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n聽親都心噏，馬尿都流埋出嚟<br />\n求下你地唔好收收埋埋，俾大家一齊幫下手<br />\n齊上齊落<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d11c6848a16a1ccfa02b4cb6199fa445f791905e","tid":1559200,"uid":33769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T16:55:20.000Z","msg":"嗰日聽晴朗真係喊咗出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f3226a61e65bf9ce909952cba4afbd0aa37b646","tid":1559200,"uid":304180,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T16:57:36.000Z","msg":"真係好撚心痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n揾緊飯腳，我都會煮下飯，快啲黎陪我食<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"217e078676eccb0c277317cbe228e10a48456287","tid":1559200,"uid":234540,"like":0,"dislike